sentences: Sean Bergin (29 June 1948 – 1 September 2012) was an avant-garde jazz saxophonist and flautist from South Africa.
Bergin was born in Durban on 29 June 1948.
From 1976 he lived in Amsterdam.
He won the VPRO/Boy Edgar Award in 2000.
